Release 0.8.18 (2020-04-04 The Compiz Reloaded Team)
==================================================================
COMPIZ-RELOADED

Add workspacenames plugin (migrated from -experimental)

Update French translations

Add a contrast differentiation mode in ADDHelper

showmouse: add option to initiate automatically on startup

First attempt at writing a plugin showing speech synthesis: highlightcontent

grid: fix issues with cycling through window sizes caused by extents

Fix grid bug that prevented certain windows (chromium based, others) from updating properly

Fix up DEBUG calls to refer to correct variables

fix make distcheck command

showmouse: Fix behavior with particles activation setting

showmouse: Fix toggling crosshairs while active

showmouse: Rewrite crosshair drawing to be affected by neg and colorfilter

wallpaper: Fix calloc call

Add and improve the bell plugin imported from https://github.com/CarterWeron/compiz-bell-plugin

